            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim the end[s] from your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> keeping the stalk[s] intact</p><p>Without cutting through the stalk[s], carefully slice the <strong>trimmed courgette[s]</strong> into thin strips, lengthways (at approx. 0.5cm intervals)</p><p>Peel lengths of the <strong>sliced courgette[s]</strong> until you have a pile of ‘courgetti’</p><p>Tip: Have a spiraliser? Use this instead!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1638259944433-x200.jpg",
