            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1638259949213-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>remaining cider vinegar </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a bowl and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>plant-based linguine carbonara </strong>and top with the <strong>remaining smoky mushrooms</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> salad</strong> to the side and drizzle over the <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
